Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cmake, qt6-base-dev, qt6-httpserver-dev, qt6-websockets-dev
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://github.com/theinvisible/tiBackup
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: tibackup
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, tibackuplib (>= 0.8.1), libqt6httpserver6, libqt6websockets6, openssl
Description: intelligent disk-based backup daemon for Linux
 tiBackup runs scheduled and hotplug-triggered backups to local and USB disks
 using rsync, with optional LUKS encryption, pre/post scripts, e-mail
 notifications and Proxmox Backup Server integration.
 .
 This package contains the root daemon (tibackupd) and its built-in,
 login-protected web UI.
